title: Latest news & Coaches Awards
itunes:title: Latest news & Coaches Awards
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- React to the latest NFL news including Gary Kubiak’s hiring and Bill Belichick’s comments on Russell Wilson. Plus, the guys review the latest coaching hires with a new awards show.
